Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Driven by the darkness in my heart, I activated The Barrier of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And lost the bond I had with my Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fell into the trap set by Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, I committed a grave sin that I can't forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Following my defeat, I lost something that was most important to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lost my partner... who was someone irreplaceable to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:01:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Torn Soul"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm peddlin' fast as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let them get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we will stay losers all our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us join your team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how I look, I was the Regional Champion of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in second place that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mai Kujaku can become your comrade, we can too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We beg ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it back safe and sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You won, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, things didn't go like what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Yugi lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you lose in a match with Doma, your soul will be taken away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said... It's already been taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't Yugi standing there perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying... You're lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please swap places and let me see my Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sacrificed himself in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just a soul\N residing in Darling's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you remain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while Darling's soul disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the original Yugi... \NDarling back to me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him {\i1}back{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner was against me using The Barrier of Orichalcos from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to activate this card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deserted my Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to {\i1}stop{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a chance to get the other Yugi back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do if you're all depressed like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of Duelists, Yugi Mutou! Where did all your {\i1}pride{\i0} go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody has won against the three Musketeers of Doma so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, stop talking rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so-sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we really don't have the power to defeat Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the center of the business district?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought since Doma's a shady group an' all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd a' been brought to a secret hideout or somethin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they really {\i1}are{\i0} hiding their motives behind such a huge organization, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to the both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all depends on what the lord that you're meeting decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try not to be too {\i1}impolite{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By your orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taken the soul of the nameless Pharaoh into our custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What da hell's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly wish I {\i1}could{\i0} praise you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've yet to accomplish this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's indeed "Yugi."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not the "Nameless Pharaoh."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two personalities in Yugi Mutou's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One being the character of Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other one is the personality of the host.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Host...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's a nameless Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personality of the host? What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have indeed defeated the nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one captured by the Barrier of Orichalcos was the personality of the vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nameless Pharaoh is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that mission, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb ol' me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, by that, I mean... Please kindly leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we're really nobodies in their eyes, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are Insector Haga and Dinosaur Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They claimed to be the first and runner up in the whole of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not "claiming to be"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really wanna get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Yugi and Jounouchi appeared, we've...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demon Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Red-Eyes was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since they've appeared, we've been humiliated constantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pride as Duelists was totally shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also wanna become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave Yugi and Jounouchi ta' us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want 'em ta' see us differently!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please also give us a portion of your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Nameless Pharaoh and Jounouchi are Duelists chosen by the Legendary Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be so easy to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we need your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had power like that, even we'd...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to obtain our power...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you must be mentally prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of defeating them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do {\i1}anything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're {\i1}really{\i0} serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, am serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what injects "life" into the cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shard of the Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shard of Orichalcos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These shards will test the darkness in your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worthy enough to join Doma,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be able to obtain these shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you two are deemed unworthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your souls will be sealed in these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Finally chickening out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hell no I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't retreat here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're afraid,\N we'll always remain worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we shall do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lets go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have that kind of ability to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, it's impossible for us to attain such powers...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're just gonna be a loser and let them take your soul away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must get hold of this power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is The Barrier of Orichalcos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, the both of you are now members of Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use any of the cards here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and create the strongest deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's simply {\i1}too{\i0} many cards here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there really all kinds of cards here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have all the cards here except for the God Cards and the Legendary Dragon cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, no God Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there are, you guys will never be able to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Even if there {\i1}is{\i0} no God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all good wit' the cards we got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insector Haga... Dinosaur Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your new-bound power, show me the defeat of Nameless Pharaoh and Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Orichalcos is now within the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yes!\N -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that the aim of Doma is to clear the history of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did say that was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way anybody could do that so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have all seen how they can do it, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be using that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, The Three Musketeers of Doma said that they needed your souls before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to use our souls as sacrifices to revive that monster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can... we go against people like them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better report this to the police or some other people who can deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Grandpa's research lab was burnt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no proof to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such absurd things... Who do you think will believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some proof left of the underwater relics...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has already been claimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Doma's doing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that if we have no proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Grandpa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you guys worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get back to sleep when I heard Rebeca crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already heard roughly the gist of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any new insights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I have not fully deciphered the cipher texts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the real identity of "Doma" may be from the ancient past...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:16:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may be the decedents from the land called Atlantis that was considered to be a paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By "Atlantis", you're referring to that rumored legendary city that was submerged underwater?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlantis is not merely a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The relics found underwater contained texts that were historical records of Atlantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which also meant that they are the history of the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlantis's history...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, Atlantis was rather highly civilized and they controlled many lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people there thus termed it as "paradise" and thought the peace would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Atlantis was suddenly destroyed by a monster that was summoned by a certain king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain... king?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There should be "darkness" that lies dormant within the deepest thresholds of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you dare say that you were a good king?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been said that Atlantis has been passing a magical stone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that has been bestowed with the power of God down to their decedents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that stone that those guys have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this is as far as I could decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you feeling so frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They purposely destroyed the professor's research lab because of all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Those cipher texts may have contained some things that were unfavorable for Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, at your mental level, such an intuition is quite remarkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most importantly, the relics are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Florida Museum acted as a base for the studying of the relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some research information that was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then there's still a chance for us to decipher the texts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lets go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll unveil the secrets of Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And rescue the other Yugi, Mai and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those're some good words, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've decided, we just got to get there before Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's quite a distance from here to Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our company's stocks have been falling since those Duel Monster's happenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And 40% of our stocks have been bought up by some unidentified person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this continues, our company...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know what's going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, haven't you guys uncovered the true background of Doma yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the capital sources that have been trying to buy up the stocks of Kaiba Corporation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mastermind must be somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you guys to find out where they are with all your might!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to Duel with that guy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand that guy's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...memento of my little brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My little brother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...killed by your company!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something like that happened to you, I would have reacted in the same way as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wish you wouldn't fight him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just thinking about his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely not a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't defeat Doma, there will be no future for both Kaiba Land and Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have a phone waiting from someone referring to themselves as "Jounouchi-{\i0}sama{\i1}."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi called?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the {\i1}deadbeat{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like we're connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba! I have a favor to ask from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be standing further away from the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sorry! Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We got some clues about Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Doma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clues are in Florida Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use your resources to bring us all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry up, the soul of the other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul of the other Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because Kaiba hates talk of the occult, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you {\i1}lost{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What are you talking about, Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess around with me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that the Duel King title I gave you on the Duel Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been taken away by some nobody we know nothing about?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've misjudged you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing more to say to a loser like you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of this, I now have one more reason to defeat you people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with... that bastard...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we can only go there ourselves now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for the professor to continue resting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll proceed first and ascertain the research lab information.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, you'll join us later when the professor has fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for us, the means of getting to Florida...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to get to the closest airport from here is by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still recuperating from the shock of losing his partner, the other Yugi is unable to stand up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to get him to snap out of it before dealing with Doma again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get to Florida Museum in order to protect the few remaining clues we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we head there by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, we can't seem to find Haga and Ryuzaki anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where they went.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Runaway Train Duel"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
